data.description: Step into this very affordable and perfectly located home. Whether your a first-time buyer or a family looking for a good home in a nice community this is a home you will want to see. This 3 bed, 2 bath  home features a fireplace, granite counter tops, recently installed handicap-accessible shower, downstairs bedroom, greenbelt and community pool for those hot summer days. It is conveniently located less than a mile from AVC and a shopping center. Like the furniture? Most of the items are for sale and can be purchased with the property! Do not hesitate to call this home could be yours just before the New Year!
